  1967 -- 1985 : Symbolic AI Era : done @ai | Logic-based reasoning, rule engines, LISP. MYCIN, Prolog, knowledge graphs.
  1967-01-01 : ELIZA Chatbot : done @ai | First conversational program by Weizenbaum at MIT
  1986 -- 2011 : Connectionism & Neural Nets : done @ai | Backprop enables multi-layer networks. SVMs, gradient boosting, early CNNs.
  1986-10-01 : Backpropagation Paper : done @ai | Rumelhart, Hinton, Williams — learning internal representations
  2012 -- 2019 : Deep Learning Explosion : done @ai | GPU compute + big data + deep nets. ImageNet moments, word2vec, ResNets.
  2012-09-30 : AlexNet — ImageNet : done @ai | GPU deep learning era begins
  2020 -- 2024 : Foundation Model Era : done @ai | Scale laws, few-shot learning, RLHF alignment. GPT-3, ChatGPT, GPT-4.
  2022-11-30 : ChatGPT Launch : done @ai | 100M users in 60 days — AI reaches mainstream
